item.title: CVE-2023-45116|2024-08-27T15:02:17.807Z -- projectworlds%20pvt.%20limited -- online%20examination%20system
item.description: Online Examination System v1.0 is vulnerable to multiple Authenticated SQL Injection vulnerabilities. The 'demail' parameter of the /update.php resource does not validate the characters received and they are sent unfiltered to the database.
